buzzer

Hardware Requirement.

-Rasberry pi kit
-Monitor
-key board
-Mouse.

Software Requirement:

→Rasberry os
→Thonny

Circuit diagram:



Buzzer :

import RPi.GPIO as GPIO
import time.
GPIO. setmode (GPIO.BCM)
GPIO. Setwarnings (False)
BUZZER = 23
buzzState = False
GPIO. Setup (BUZZER, GPIO.OUT)
While True:
buzzState = not buzzState
GPIO. Output ( BUZZER, buzzState)
time.sleep(1)
